  "text": "In the presence of heterogeneity, subgroup analysis was performed based on the measurement methods or the type of exercise. Besides, sensitivity analysis was carried out to evaluate the influence of a single study to the overall estimate. Publication bias was estimated through Begg's test and Egger's linear regression, with P0.10 consumed as an indication of publication bias. [CITATION_1] All analyses were conducted using Review Manager Version 5.3 (Cochrane Collaboration, Copenhagen, Denmark) and Stata 12.0 (College Station, TX, USA).",
